nodes.text: Romm Zqar was a Yuuzhan Vong commander, in charge of the landings on Coruscant during the attack on the planet in 27 ABY. He was killed, along with 25,000 other Yuuzhan Vong warriors, by Chief of State Borsk Fey'lya's dejarik-inspired detonation blast, which was originally intended for Warmaster Tsavong Lah.
